# StyleSense Fashion Review Predictor
ML pipeline for predicting product recommendations from reviews.

## Features
- Text preprocessing (fashion-specific cleaning)
- TF-IDF feature engineering
- Scikit-learn Pipeline + GridSearchCV tuning
- Logistic Regression classifier

## Usage
Update 'reviews.csv' path and run script. Expects 'review_text' and 'recommendation' (0/1) columns.

## Results Example
Accuracy: ~87% on test set.
